      "content": "i just mean... if i'm already so invisible, it feels like it wouldn't even be a big deal to just make it official. like, if i just disappeared, would it actually be a tragedy, or would it just be a quiet, non-eventful moment for everyone? i feel like nobody even deserves to notice me.",
